== Amawal ==
llan kraḍ iɣbula mqqurnin n umawal ɣ tutlayt tajapunit, ''yamaṭu kuṭuba'' (大和言葉) nɣ d ''wagu'' (和語), ''kangu'' (漢語), d ''gayraygu'' (外来語).

Asidf n umawal nna d yuckan ɣ tutlayin n [[Uṛuppa]], ''gayraygu'', ibda d urṭṭal zɣ [[Tutlayt Tabṛṭqqizt|tabṛṭqqizt]] ɣ tasut tiss 16. Dffir, ibda uṛṭṭal zɣ [[Tutlayt tahulanḍit|thulanḍiyt]] (ar as ttinin s tjapubit: ''rangaku'', 蘭学) ɣ uzmz n Iḍo. Lliɣ tnnurẓm Japun ɣ uzmz n Miji ɣ tasut tiss 19 ibda uṛṭṭal zɣ tutlayin ad: [[tutlayt talimant|talimant]], [[Tutlayt Tafṛanṣiṣt|tafṛansist]] d [[tutlayt tanglizt|tinglizt]]. Ɣilad tutlayt tanglizt ad igan aɣbalu izwarn nna yakkan tiguriwin i tutlayt tajapunit.

== Tinml ==
Tisdawiyin timqranin ɣ umaḍal as ssaqrant tutlayt tajapunit. Ula kra n tinmal n imẓyanen ar ssaqrant tutlayt ad. Ɣayad ibadl bahra f uzmz dat n uqryan amaḍlan wiss sin, lliɣ ɣar 65 n umirikni issn i ad yara d ad yaqqra d ad irms tutlayt ad.<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20110623220241/http://www.c-span.org/Events/Sotomayor-Denzel-Washington-GE-CEO-Speak-to-Graduates/10737421758-10/ Sotomayor, Denzel Washington, GE CEO Speak to Graduates.]</ref>

